name: There is no right time
description:
Time is the fairest element in this world. We only have 1440 minutes a day. Everyone has the same opportunity. However, we waiting for the right time, keep waiting and waiting without making any progress. 

I don't think there is a perfect time, there is only preparation and luck. Because every moment is the right time if we are ready enough for that.

(2000x2000)
